summary:
Hey, you know what's the best way to relax after a month of art challenges? ANIMATING BANDAGES OF COURSE! 8D I've
 been playing...
caption:
Hey, you know what’s the best way to relax after a month of art challenges? ANIMATING BANDAGES OF COURSE! 8D

I’ve been playing with the idea of animating Krator with a voice line I thought suited him the most. I’d like to imagine Krator with a gruff but soft voice. I think Geralt from The Witcher would fit him the most.

Hope you guys like it!
